# MellyTrade desktop (Tauri) build environment — EXAMPLE ONLY.
#
# Copy to `.env.desktop` (git-ignored) OR rely on scripts/build_desktop_tauri.ps1,
# which sets these in the build process environment for you.
#
# This file contains NO secrets. The backend URL below is the public hosted
# Render endpoint. Do NOT add API keys, tokens, account IDs, or broker
# credentials here or in any committed env file.

# Hosted backend API base used by the bundled desktop frontend build.
# The desktop app has no local backend; all data comes from this read-only host.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://alpha-data-scraper-ai.onrender.com/api
